title: Fans Only ( Migos interview)
itunes:title: Fans Only ( Migos interview)
description:
Today on the show we celebrated the biggest hip hop group the Migos as they stopped by to speak on their new album Culture 3 and other business ventures. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a hospital worker who simply does not have repsect for the dead as she took a dead patients bank card and used it to by chips out the vending machine. Also, Angela helped some listeners during "Ask Yee" and one of the callers happen to be a 60 year old woman doing something strange for some change!
